  <code>legaldisclaimer.html</code>, <code>privacy-app.html</code> and
  <code>terms-app.html</code> documents.

==Verification==

Reviewers can reproduce the claims in this DIP locally:

<pre>
git clone https://github.com/DigiByte-Core/DGBio.git
cd DGBio
git checkout redesign-2026
npx serve .
</pre>

Then, in a separate terminal:

<pre>
npx lighthouse http://localhost:3000/ \
  --preset=desktop --only-categories=performance,accessibility,best-practices,seo \
  --chrome-flags="--headless"
</pre>

Expected results, median of three runs (mobile profile, throttled Slow
4G), are listed in the table under
[[#Performance, accessibility and SEO|Specification &gt; Performance,
accessibility and SEO]]. Locale parity can be verified with:

<pre>
node tools/sync-locales.mjs --check
</pre>

which exits non-zero if any locale homepage drifts from the English
source structure.

